    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''A bullet was fired at freedom of thought and democratic life in Turkey. Once again, dark hands have chosen our country and spilled blood in Istanbul to achieve their dark goals.''</p>
        <p>RECEP TAYYIP ERDOGAN, Turkey's prime minister, on the killing of an outspoken newspaper editor. [A3]</p>
      </block>
